ZH: 我明天要买车票回家。
EN: I need to buy a ticket to go home tomorrow.

ZH: 请问这趟列车的车票多少钱？
EN: Excuse me, how much is the ticket for this train?

ZH: 我的车票是纸的，不是电子的。
EN: My ticket is paper, not electronic.

ZH: 你可以在售票处买车票。
EN: You can buy tickets at the ticket office.

ZH: 买车票的人很多，要排队。
EN: There are many people buying tickets, so you need to line up.

ZH: 请确保保存好你的车票。
EN: Please make sure to keep your ticket safe.

ZH: 我刚刚丢了我的车票，能再给我一张吗？
EN: I just lost my ticket, can I get another one?

ZH: 这是我第一次买火车票。
EN: This is my first time buying a train ticket.

ZH: 我的车票日期错了，怎么办？
EN: The date on my ticket is wrong, what should I do?

ZH: 我可以用手机买车票吗？
EN: Can I buy a ticket with my phone?

ZH: 请查看车票上的座位号。
EN: Please check the seat number on your ticket.

ZH: 火车票很便宜，我们可以多坐一次。
EN: Train tickets are cheap, we can take an extra ride.

ZH: 我已经准备好车票了，我们可以出发了。
EN: I already have the tickets ready, we can leave now.

ZH: 这张车票是单程的，不可以再返回。
EN: This ticket is for one-way only, you cannot return with it.

ZH: 请出示你的车票和身份证。
EN: Please show your ticket and ID card.

ZH: 我将在售票窗口领取我预定的车票。
EN: I will collect my reserved ticket at the ticket window.

ZH: 这个车票适用于所有的公交车。
EN: This ticket is valid for all buses.

ZH: 请在进站前检查你的车票。
EN: Please check your ticket before entering the station.

ZH: 是否需要车票来乘坐这路公共汽车？
EN: Do you need a ticket to take this bus?

ZH: 他们的车票已经过期了，不能用了。
EN: Their tickets have expired and cannot be used.
